      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "R"                  to   w-cnt-cor-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-cor-000      thru vis-lin-cor-999        .
